deParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523214342-0rbpg8a","updated":"20240523214342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240523214342-j5lcm9a.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240523214345-3f4jqih","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240523214345-3f4jqih","updated":"20240523214413"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5. SAML 的身份声明符咒"}]},{"ID":"20240523214414-ri440od","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523214414-ri440od","updated":"20240523214435"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后登场的是SAML（Security Assertion Markup Language）。这位魔法师擅长使用XML文书形式传输身份声明，用户在身份提供方登录后，会收到一份魔法信件——SAML断言，凭借这份断言，可以解锁众多服务提供商的入口。"}]},{"ID":"20240523214437-fml10kp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523214437-fml10kp","updated":"20240523214444"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就像巫师们互相发送的身份证明信函，有了它，无论走到哪个魔法学院，都能被迅速识别并接纳。"}]},{"ID":"20240523214531-3y9uczg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523214531-3y9uczg","updated":"20240523214531"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240523214531-hb2oag8.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240523214542-wkv8tso","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240523214542-wkv8tso","updated":"20240523214553"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6. 结尾"}]},{"ID":"20240523224426-hiqw932","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523224426-hiqw932","updated":"20240523224426"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当我们明白了这四位魔法师各自的神通之后，面对具体的业务场景，该如何做出最优选择呢？这就涉及到了安全性、易用性、集成难易度以及成本等多个考量因素。"}]},{"ID":"20240523224426-j6om1c5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523224426-j6om1c5","updated":"20240523224426"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"       比如，如果你身处一家需要高度安全和严格控制的大型组织，可能会倾向于选择SAML，因为它提供了强大的安全性和严格的控制手段。而在追求灵活快捷的互联网产品开发中，OAuth2.0与OIDC可能是更好的搭档，它们能够方便地与其他第三方服务集成，并优化用户体验。"}]},{"ID":"20240523224426-54vaanf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523224426-54vaanf","updated":"20240523224426"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"       亲爱的读者朋友，你在实际项目中是否也曾面临过选择单点登录技术的困境？面对不同业务需求，又是如何权衡利弊、因地制宜来选用最适合的方案呢？快在留言区分享你的实战心得，我们一同探讨，让这场关于单点登录的“魔法”对话持续发酵吧！"}]},{"ID":"20240523224426-lgxa49y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240523224426-lgxa49y","updated":"20240523224433"}}]}